2026-05-14T01:13:01.1281614Z 217        <!--
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1282258Z 218            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1283218Z 219            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1284353Z 220            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1285245Z 221            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1286250Z 222            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1287072Z 223            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1287966Z 224            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-14T01:13:01.1288814Z 225            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
